narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Very low key. It's as intensive as you would like to make it, which is great. I had a really hard schedule, so I was not able to devote much time to my senior project and was (hopefully) not penalized for it.
You have to take this if you are an astro major. So enjoy!
This class is required for the major, so if you're majoring in it, then you'll be taking it. That said, Prof. Fischer is laid back and will let you work on your project without any problems.
